	<div class="article-detail-bd">
			<div class="excerpt">
				所谓的车迷狂欢，是指你可以摸得到梦幻座驾的那种。
			</div>
		<div class="detail">
				<!-- 普通文章 -->
				<p>
	<span>古德伍德，是位于英国西</span><span><span>塞萨克斯郡</span></span><span>的特色小镇。这里有世界闻名的赛马场、古德伍德复古艺术节、古德伍德咖啡艺术节，还有世界上规模最大、历史最悠久的赛车盛事古德伍德速度节。</span> 
</p>
<p>
	<span>“假如你是一名</span><span><span>汽车</span></span><span>发烧友，那么古德伍德便是你的圣地。”红牛车队首席技术执行官安德里亚</span><span>·</span><span>纽维曾这样形容。</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201506/06e355cdacb2.jpg" title=" " alt=" " height="400" width="640" /> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;">
	<span>上周末，这项一年一度的车迷狂欢在古德</span><span>伍德开幕，</span><span>今年的主题是“马力全开无所畏惧：极限边缘的赛车”。<span></span>梅赛德斯、红牛、<span></span></span><span><span>法拉利</span></span><span>、</span><span><span>迈凯伦</span></span><span>和威<span></span>廉姆斯五家顶级 <span>F1 </span>一级方程式车队携最新的赛车前来，现役 <span>F1 </span>车手马萨和莱科宁也来到现场。<span></span> <br />
</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201506/d46e7b886504.jpg" title=" " alt=" " height="480" width="640" /> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;">
	<span>(</span><span>迈凯轮车手简森</span><span>·</span><span>巴顿成为了古德伍德的熟面孔</span><span>)</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;">
	<span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201506/78c9a245b2e4.jpg" title=" " alt=" " height="427" width="640" /> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;">
	<span>布鲁克兰围场展示的是赛车家族系列中的经典车型，在这里游客们可以近距离欣赏到这些传奇车型的工艺细节。</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;">
	<span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201506/a0ae95817a39.jpg" title=" " alt=" " height="427" width="640" /><span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<br />
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201506/6739db9a8b80.jpg" title=" " alt=" " height="627" width="940" /> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201506/9a8e0eb22ea8.jpg" title=" " alt=" " height="427" width="640" /> 
</p>
<p>
	<span>每年的卡地亚“豪华风格”汽车设计竞赛单位将评选出当届速度节上最为唯美、奢华的跑车。</span> 
</p>
<p>
	<span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201506/5f85bc4846ec.jpg" title=" " alt=" " height="383" width="640" /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p>
	今年获胜的是 1937 年款 Talbot-Lago T150-C S Teardrop 天使之泪，其美艳的程度简直让人落泪。以下为其他获奖作品：
</p>
<p>
	<span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;">
	<span>Sweeping Statements</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;">
	<span>1939 Delahaye 165 Cabriolet
(Peter Mullin)</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201506/0ccb6e7af4ea.jpg" title=" " alt=" " height="427" width="640" /> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;">
	<span>Modern Classics</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;">
	<span>2011 Eagle Speedster
(Henry Pearman)</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;">
	<span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201506/be31d9d6f009.jpg" title=" " alt=" " height="421" width="640" /> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:left;">
	<span>A Sporting Advantage</span> 
</p>
<p>
	<span>1931
Alfa Romeo&nbsp; 8C 2300MM (Eric Heerema)</span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201506/4dc3584d3f38.jpg" title=" " alt=" " height="426" width="640" /> 
</p>
<p>
	<span>Goddess of the Highway<br />
1957 Citroën DS19 Berline (Wenzel Gelpke)</span> 
</p>
<p>
	<span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201506/a575279cdaba.jpg" title=" " alt=" " height="426" width="640" /> 
</p>
<p>
	<span>英国跑车与赛车生产商路特斯，或译作莲花汽车 <span>(Lotus
Cars)</span> 也是古德伍德的常客，素来以纯粹的驾驶乐趣和轻量化的设计闻名。</span> 
</p>
<p>
	<span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201506/7161b80c046c.jpg" title=" " alt=" " height="426" width="640" /> 
</p>
<p>
	<span>本次速度节，发布了一款新车型—— “<span>three-eleven</span>” ，是目前莲花旗下最快的跑车，预计明年二月交付，限量生产 <span>311</span> 部，售价约为 <span>82,000</span> 英镑起。</span> 
</p>
<p>
	<span><span> </span></span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201506/fd3ba613968c.jpg" title=" " alt=" " height="426" width="640" /> 
</p>
<p>
	<span><span>three-eleven</span> 使用超轻量化车身，座舱无顶棚设计极为纯粹，采用由碳纤维复合材料制造的轻桶形座椅。出色的功率<span>-</span>重量比使得它能够在<span> 3 </span>秒内完成 <span>0-100 km/h </span>的加速，极速则可达<span> 290km/h</span>。</span> 
</p>
<p>
	<span> </span> 
</p>
<p style="text-align:center;">
	<img src="/uploads/image/201506/b0b8979c9e2c.jpg" title=" " alt=" " height="426" width="640" /><span> </span> 
</p>
<p>
	无挡风设计则流露出肆无忌惮的姿态，毫无疑问，驾驶者需要一个头盔才可以驾驭激进的 three-eleven，以此抵挡冲向面部的高速气流。
</p>
<p>
	(图片来自 grrc.goodwood.com)<br />
<span><span></span></span> 
</p>
